snippet.title: INNER Anthology - Trailer - Now on Itch.io
snippet.description:
Get INNER now on itch for only $1.00! https://darkstonedigital.itch.io/inner

INNER is a mini-game created during a 3 day long game jam live on Twitch by solo game developer Brian Clarke. Wander through your mind and piece together memories. Face the fear you've been running from.

Be sure to subscribe for more game dev related videos and updates! https://bit.ly/2x7qiaL

TWITTER: https://twitter.com/DSDigitalDev
TWITCH: https://www.twitch.tv/darkstonedigital
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/join/DarkStoneDigital

-------------------------------------- My Setup
* AMD Ryzen 7 2700 - https://amzn.to/2YIJ6cg

* GeForce GTX 1070 - https://amzn.to/2XxbvFG
* Dual Asus 24" - https://amzn.to/2S10Kpe
* Cintiq 22 HD - https://amzn.to/2XyVXwy
* Logitech 720 - https://amzn.to/2LajSAG
